課程概述 Course Description
       本課程為英語授課，請詳英文簡介。Start from quantum mechanical axioms, illustrate the main concepts of quantum mechanics, and introduce related important topics.
    

課程學習目標 Course Objectives
To provide the principles, concepts and methodologies of quantum mechanics.To cultivate skills at formulating and solving physics problems.To develop the self-discipline and work habits to succeed in the real world. 

課程進度 Course Outline


週次 Week進度說明 Progress Description
1Density Matrix2Quantum Teleportation3Schrodinger Equation in EM Fields (I)4Schrodinger Equation in EM Fields (II)5Spin (I)6Spin (II)7Addition of Angular Momentum (I) 8Addition of Angular Momentum (II) 9Midterm Exam10The Variational and WKB Methods (I)11The Variational and WKB Methods (II)12Perturbation Theory (I)13Perturbation Theory (II)14Perturbation Theory (III)15Scattering Theory (I) 16Scattering Theory (II) 17Open Quantum Sysytems18Final Exam. 

　以上每週進度教師可依上課情況做適度調整。The schedule may be subject to change.


